                                        "audioUrl":  "https://wow.zamimg.com/sound-ids/live/enus/59/2000443/VO_801_Brann_Bronzebeard_44_M.ogg",
                                        "text":  "I've heard stories about the power o' N'Zoth's minions, but I never thought I'd see one. Honestly, I hope I never do again.",
